{{Top|leg}}
'''Vortexlex''', or '''Vorese''', was the native language of the [[Vor]] species from [[Vortex/Legends|Vortex]]. Vorese used soft chirps, lilting squawks, and trilling whistles to form a melodic language to hear.

Vorese had its own alphabet, using diamond shapes and swirling lines to represent individual letters.

Most Vors were fluent in both Vorese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

